frames.caption: A futuristic armored figure stands confidently in front of a traditional Japanese building under a full moon. Cherry blossoms frame the scene, while shadowy figures wielding swords can be seen in the background.
frames.description: The scene depicts a blend of futuristic and traditional elements, with a high-tech armored character in a Japanese setting. The atmosphere is tense and dramatic, enhanced by the moonlit night and the presence of armed figures.
